{"tid":1669332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上的士後問司機支唔支持五大訴求","createTime":"2019-10-22T13:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T14:32:26.000Z","uid":155401,"like":31,"dislike":195,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"e746a5ab39efa5ceafb146c02b6e175344521817","tid":1669332,"uid":155401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:19:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟老豆係做的士司機嘅<br />\n岩先聽佢講尼排有啲的士司機做街客接左我地手足之後<br />\n俾手足問支唔支持五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而好多司機都驚俾人搞事所以都話支持。<br />\n但係講完支持之後就會俾手足要求坐霸王的，啲司機驚畀人打所以都只好硬食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上嘅野都係聽我老豆講嘅，fc 唔到， 我都相信我地手足唔係啲會要挾人嘅人，但係出得去就係代表緊我地每個人，希望唔好為左啲小便宜而減少肯支持我地嘅人<br />\n記得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be HUMBLE</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知冇證冇據會畀人負皮，但係希望大家知道多個支持我地嘅人好過多個敵人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4863b9a3503a356d59c980dba53b23173493307","tid":1669332,"uid":57322,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:20:16.000Z","msg":"分化撚，扑"},{"pid":"0ced8778697fc364a7a6f6fcbf96d0a4a4889882","tid":1669332,"uid":167548,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:20:22.000Z","msg":"一聽就知是藍絲故仔 <br />\n你啊爸信就算啦 你都信埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7021ed56417c79cc114b2edec900f3cd05b814","tid":1669332,"uid":35456,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d2052a4909a3b9f3e707df55e2cb57b1ccb47b1","tid":1669332,"uid":227588,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:20:27.000Z","msg":"有都一定係藍絲，唔會錯"},{"pid":"01991265d258a5d96033a12dbdc1e3c152ef030e","tid":1669332,"uid":1